plyTime":"2017-01-24T13:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而想知點解safety video經常強調要戴好自己個oxygen mask先好幫其他人<br />\n間間航空公司段片都係咁講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為如果急降得幾十秒係清醒 之後有機會會控制唔到自己 如果幫左人先 就唔夠時間幫自己 所以應該每個人都幫左自己先 好似係"},{"pid":"0688b7d4dc30584c7f8637ed41f611ea3562a6fc","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而想知點解safety video經常強調要戴好自己個oxygen mask先好幫其他人<br />\n間間航空公司段片都係咁講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為如果急降得幾十秒係清醒 之後有機會會控制唔到自己 如果幫左人先 就唔夠時間幫自己 所以應該每個人都幫左自己先 好似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇幾高，40000尺得十秒度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0c31a4f6eb8f993eaf0e5baa8ad3a12de0851e","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解起飛同降落要閂遮光板</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落咗點睇出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bff233911bc7ca65ee902648bcd96fb8a638a55","tid":93410,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁點解起飛同降落要閂遮光板</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落咗點睇出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗佢想講開。<br />\n之前上網查過，可以及時睇到機翼，機身，engine 有冇異常"},{"pid":"8accbf41aa76b5dd837c87e2e57b988f0f6470c2","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁點解起飛同降落要閂遮光板</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落咗點睇出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗佢想講開。<br />\n之前上網查過，可以及時睇到機翼，機身，engine 有冇異常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實主要係怕啲傻仔懶醒，個面着火個面跳slides<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d87dd9c82558b927f5923f972085cd88364a41","tid":93410,"uid":6083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為飛機受規定要