e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解張櫈要較直？怕我撞親？</blockquote><br />\n起飛降落時最多意外，要減少你係撞擊中對脊骨傷害</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n同埋驚有意外會頂住左後面走唔到<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好似係</span>"},{"pid":"9a9d799f16ee1f27c8f54fc620844402f3a15691","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解起飛時起機翼到會見到氣流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWing tip vortex is greatest when flying at low speed and dirty configuration"},{"pid":"a93de72325a1844b2b67b61c1064676f1c765ffe","tid":93410,"uid":5485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為飛機受規定要參加地球一小時行動<br />\n但航空公司長期反對 話會不安<br />\n之後改為起飛降落一分鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一打唔洗找"},{"pid":"7006c0c4b152ceb246c91a840502a170c2dbaeb5","tid":93410,"uid":73996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"機倉光暗度要match番出面<br />\ne.g. 夜晚take off/landing要dim cabin light, 日頭就唔駛<br />\n<br />\n利申：男空姐"},{"pid":"ebb1ff3dabefd2b6fbd249a74d2729c04bbf6e0f","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機倉光暗度要match番出面<br />\ne.g. 夜晚take off/landing要dim cabin light, 日頭就唔駛<br />\n<br />\n利申：男空姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n茄航啲女易唔易食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad8b595ee6df3c3e8006b0401eddf4e6b5fe996","tid":93410,"uid":8756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n起飛降落時最多意外，要減少你係撞擊中對脊骨傷害</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n同埋驚有意外會頂住左後面走唔到<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好似係</span></blockquote><br />\n似係呢個多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87b13675f5ddaa2e612ab72f4a5c157476864e6","tid":93410,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解起飛時起機翼到會見到氣流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWing tip vortex is greatest when flying at low speed and dirty configuration</blockquote><br />\n但唔係應該downwash嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望果陣佢冇向下"},{"pid":"66f63a2628c2dafd411d3aa7205c12116fd1fe10","tid":93410,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"點解 起飛同降落會高危d??<br />\n<br />\n不過我信係 次次降落d氣流勁到 衝落雲層次次都chok到我大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69135c79b38fdc37d8181315a37193f7c680af75","tid":93410,"uid":2045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解起飛時起機翼到會見到氣流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWing tip vortex is greatest when flying at low speed and dirty configuration</blockquote><br />\n但唔係應該downwash嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望果陣佢冇向下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪講緊contrail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為機翼面氣壓低, vapour會凝結 所以會有contrail<br />\n應該就係你講既氣流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非aviation degree 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20800bf19893c1a4d860e431116173c7645c03c7","tid":93410,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWing tip vortex is greatest when flying at low speed and dirty configuration</blockquote><br />\n但唔係應該downwash嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望果陣佢冇向下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪講緊contrail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為機翼面氣壓低, vapour會凝結 所以會有contrail<br />\n應該就係你講既氣流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非aviation degree 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來叫contrail"},{"pid":"ac60935ea97a5118f26592bbedf1f8dc582c9bb9","tid":93410,"uid":2045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解 起飛同降落會高危d??<br />\n<br />\n不過我信係 次次降落d氣流勁到 衝落雲層次次都chok到我大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊咩高危d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛機過左唔知幾多萬呎（對流層 好似係）<br />\n上面既climate會stable好多<br />\n但landing個陣會落番去 所以會feel到勁氣流<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b0c8bb96b522313a4cba1a19ec6fc787a2c66b","tid":93410,"uid":2045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n但唔係應該downwash嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望果陣佢冇向下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪講緊contrail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為機翼面氣壓低, vapour會凝結 所以會有contrail<br />\n應該就係你講既氣流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非aviation degree 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來叫contrail</blockquote><br />\n唔知岩唔岩架 平時當興趣睇下only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6600986ffa015223528835706ef4a9d9611ab6","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解起飛時起機翼到會見到氣流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWing tip vortex is greatest when flying at low speed and dirty configuration</blockquote><br />\n但唔係應該downwash嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望果陣佢冇向下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWingtip vortices produces downwash of air <br />\n一樣啫<br />\n<br />\n如果淨睇take off深入啲係因為個AOA 上升pressure 會drop，到dew point 咪有condensation"},{"pid":"2d3733d46c9242bcaeb861d675c066109ef67032","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWing tip vortex is greatest when flying at low speed and dirty configuration</blockquote><br />\n但唔係應該downwash嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望果陣佢冇向下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪講緊contrail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為機翼面氣壓低, vapour會凝結 所以會有contrail<br />\n應該就係你講既氣流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非aviation degree 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nContrail 通常形容cruising 個時形成嘅man made cloud"},{"pid":"b3ee8010717bb0eebb5891a269d4278727743620","tid":93410,"uid":43234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解 起飛同降落會高危d??<br />\n<br />\n不過我信係 次次降落d氣流勁到 衝落雲層次次都chok到我大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為landing 通常人手land ，個機頭柒部機咪跟住柒pilot induced turbulence <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b7122687134e6c73843be5d53be4130a8be3fc","tid":93410,"uid":39154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解 起飛同降落會高危d??<br />\n<br />\n不過我信係 次次降落d氣流勁到 衝落雲層次次都chok到我大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為landing 通常人手land ，個機頭柒部機咪跟住柒pilot induced turbulence <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為巡航係"},{"pid":"b9abf38d009ece035ce02d3bde19211f49de72e1","tid":93410,"uid":39154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote]點解 起飛同降落會高危d??<br />\n<br />\n不過我信係 次次降落d氣流勁到 衝落雲層次次都chok到我大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為landing 通常人手land ，個機頭柒部機咪跟住柒pilot induced turbulence <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為巡航係幾萬米高空既平流層，大氣環境相對比較穩定，氣流影響比較少<br />\n起飛降落去返對流層，受到地面風力風向影響，風切變之類，環境複雜就容易chok<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"6fd96784e17e345a5fabfdd59446fdf7adc372b3","tid":93410,"uid":38102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"試過好多次都都係開晒燈咁<br />\n冇咁緊張 而且係落左都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}